  <brief_title>GTX-RT in Borderline Resectable Pancreatic Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Validation of a Radiation Response Signature in Borderline Resectable Pancreatic Cancer Patients Treated With Induction Chemotherapy Followed by Stereotactic Body Radiation Therapy (SBRT)</official_title>
